+
+Status: prepared.
+
+Scope:
+- Reads `prototype_live_execution_plan.json`.
+- Executes the live controlled local prototype.
+- Writes local sqlite dev SQL record.
+- Creates/recreates dedicated local Qdrant collection.
+- Upserts Qdrant point.
+- Queries Qdrant.
